access.onlineAccessDetails: Companies can be searched by legal name or registration number. Search results provide registration number, legal entity's name, registration body, registration date, company status etc. There is English interface, yet not complete. Company registration number will be under 'Регистрационный номер' header.

description.en: Information is available only in Belarusian language, contains Registration number, Registration authority, Date of registration, etc.

name.en: Unified State Register of Legal Entities and Individual Entrepreneurs (Ministry of Justice of the Republic of Belarus)
